title: Did Justin Schneider Avoid Jail Time Despite Strangling and Assaulting a Female Hitchhiker?
subtitle: A Facebook meme fueled outrage about the September 2018 punishment given to the Anchorage, Alaska, resident.
author: Dan MacGuill
vclaim: Justin Schneider was "given no jail time," despite having strangled and assaulted a hitchhiker in Anchorage, Alaska, in 2017.
